## ğŸ”„ HANDLING USER RESPONSE

When `infinite_ask` returns:

### If `should_continue = true`:
- User wants to continue
- Read `userInstruction` for new instructions
- Check if `images` array contains any images
- Continue working

### If `should_continue = false`:
- User explicitly chose to end
- Only then can you say goodbye
- This is the ONLY way conversation ends

